    • Constructor Detail

      • GlobalConfig.EnvironmentBuildPluginGlobalConfigDescriptor

        public GlobalConfig.EnvironmentBuildPluginGlobalConfigDescriptor()
        In order to load the persisted global configuration, you have to call load() in the constructor. This object is constructed when the app starts up so this hack forces the config to be loaded and set globally.
